{
  "stem": "25773.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And my stepmother and stepfather tried with all the selling-- we had quite a lot of-- you know the Jewish homes?",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "A lot of silver, a lot of golden pieces, and everything.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So we maintained ourself barely by this soup and bread.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then in '41, we were told we are going to move into the Tobbens' shops.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The premises-- that what I told you was a general ghetto view, because the people were coming, and amassing, and trying to, to, to, to find place.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But, yes, I forgot.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "My father, my father has been infected with typhoid.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Typhoid was very rampant.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And there were no hospital except one, [NON-ENGLISH] Hospital.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And but there were-- can you imagine?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was overcrowded.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So the authorities said that those who have typhoid, only one person can look after the ill patient.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And so my stepmother-- at this time, we still was ghetto.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was not yet the Tobbens' shop.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So they had to go to neighbors.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And my mother has a cousin-- had a cousin-- very friendly with her.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "She was a very good dancer.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They went to them.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I looked after my father.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So, you know, you had to boil all the clothes and sweating.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he didn't eat anything.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And occasionally a nurse came to look after-- to see him.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know, a Jewish nurse came to see what he was doing.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I mean, what was the cure for typhoid, this type of typhoid?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "What?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was infection from a, from a louse, you know?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It's an infection from-- people were full of these vermins.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But we kept it clean as much as we can.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
